{"model": "Devstral Small 2 24B", "runtime": "mlx", "prompt_name": "code_lru_cache__t3_direct", "prompt_tokens": 112, "generation_tokens": 143, "prompt_tps": 518.873040941343, "generation_tps": 39.49295647163365, "peak_memory_gb": 13.529404524, "wall_time_sec": 3.884114333006437, "output": "```python\ndef __init__(self, capacity: int):\n    self.capacity = capacity\n    self.cache = {}\n    self.queue = []\n\ndef get(self, key: int) -> int:\n    if key not in self.cache:\n        return -1\n    self.queue.remove(key)\n    self.queue.append(key)\n    return self.cache[key]\n\ndef put(self, key: int, value: int):\n    if key in self.cache:\n        self.queue.remove(key)\n    elif len(self.cache) >= self.capacity:\n        lru_key = self.queue.pop(0)\n        del self.cache[lru_key]\n    self.cache[key] = value\n    self.queue.append(key)\n```", "error": null, "prompt_hash": "e594f8996a66", "quant": "4bit"}
